text: Elections were held for the first time for the five members of the Electoral College of Sint Eustatius on 20 March 2019. ==Results== ===Electoral College=== {| class=wikitable style=text-align:right !Party !Votes !% !Seats !+/– |- |align=left|Democratic Party||366||||5|| |- |align=left|Invalid/blank votes||8||–||–||– |- |align=left|Total||374||100||5||0 |- |align=left|Registered voters/turnout||1,878|| ||–||– |- |align=left colspan=5|Source: The Daily Herald |} The Electoral College will vote for members of the Senate on 27 May 2019 as part of the wider Senate elections. ==References== Sint Eustatius Category:2019 in Sint Eustatius Sint Eustatius Category:Elections in Sint Eustatius
